</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uexedor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Exedor</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(1/7/01 5:07:37 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.westol.com/~target/exepic/exedor.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What crystal cavern quest</span><hr size=1> Well I did this quest and I wanted to warn everyone about how buggy it is. But still i think it has the potential to be a very cool quest.<br>
