i was bound like 40 feet away so i immediately memmed sow snare and scoriae and pounced on fergul , beat him senseless (with help from some bystanders that jumped in) and HIS BODY WENT POOF the instant he died the broodmother, who was stomping towards me still very healthy, also went poof *the moment fergul died*<br>
